The Association is a member of PensionsEurope.&#xd;
&#xd;
PensionsEurope's role is to develop a good EU framework that promotes workplace pensions in Europe and achieves good member outcomes. PensionsEurope works closely with the EU institutions and relevant stakeholders and is the only association that focuses exclusively on pensions.&#xd;
&#xd;
PensionsEurope has 23 Members in 16 EU Member States and 4 other countries. Together they provide pensions for about 80 million European citizens and own assets of around ? 3.2 trillion.
